Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.50,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Just come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.64,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:10.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's teach him how fun karuta can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.22,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.16,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged me all the way here by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.91,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.95,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,The karuta club is short on members, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.41,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,So you just need to bolster head count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.73,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Look elsewhere, if you don't care who joins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I do care who joins!
