Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Just play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that you'll be hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.06,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.53,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,If I had time to play karuta, \NI would be studying instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:47.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-kun, you want to \Nbecome smarter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.81,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is a mental game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,First, you have to memorize \Nthe positions of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:57.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The fastest people can memorize all \Nof them in five- no, three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:02.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger memorization skills will \Nhelp you with your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.85,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize the positions?\N  Of every card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.45,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.60,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
