Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.05,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most basic step!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.46,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,No grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you right now!
